{"tid":990314,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得香港人聽得太少歌","createTime":"2019-01-21T12:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T04:46:28.000Z","uid":88117,"like":16,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"05ab8922ef0083ef714e1409dce7f9171aecb27d","tid":990314,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"見身邊好多人聽嘅都係來不開啲大路野，真係好鬼悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以決定自己整啲playlist比大家平時做野or訓教聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等大家聽多啲歌<br />\n順便幫啲indie宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲list會分左唔同mood<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9i9aPd7MVME&amp;t=411s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9i9aPd7MVME%26t%3D411s&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=77ec4f0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9i9aPd7MVME&amp;t=411s</a><br />\n呢個moody啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xp9H2s46K_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxp9H2s46K_I&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d938915a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xp9H2s46K_I</a><br />\n呢條就開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iuBnalOUx9c&amp;t=2390s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiuBnalOUx9c%26t%3D2390s&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7bbe38be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iuBnalOUx9c&amp;t=2390s</a><br />\n呢個就感覺chill啲<br />\n<br />\n之後都會keep住update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家閒時都聽下，認識多啲好音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S.每條片嘅圖都會自己整，未到絕景應該都唔用人地啲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6490984980994ec7aa1bbc6cd93fdbc2fe04318","tid":990314,"uid":146063,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"關唔關你事？"},{"pid":"96251ba5af3148354846f121aed6ed3383c7ea1e","tid":990314,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"聽富林六大惡魔就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a5181a34fd5dbff7c154229ffabe925f9b112b","tid":990314,"uid":88117,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6490984980994ec7aa1bbc6cd93fdbc2fe04318","tid":990314,"uid":146063,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"關唔關你事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"聽下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb47ebbf86ec9b05a5ab83bc0b91fb9f1685b0b6","tid":990314,"uid":52571,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"你啲歌仲撚悶"},{"pid":"fcbd30e4e26981cd09a1333cf179bd93f71c16b7","tid":990314,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96251ba5af3148354846f121aed6ed3383c7ea1e","tid":990314,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"聽富林六大惡魔就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"背曬可以值人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e4e0492cf285f906923bfed18c9b934acdb42c","tid":990314,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"要入腦就要口水歌<br />\n唔口水歌又冇人識<br />\n唔怪得d歌手既"},{"pid":"d813c8366ee4a123358eec4f29ad733042ab7771","tid":990314,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite